A simple C/S prototype for deploy_manager.

For convenience purpose
    both server and client are in the same program.
    C/S communication are limited

Design considerations
    try to use jsocket form jlib
    can use mashal/unmarshal or other method to pass command

Dependencies
    boost program-options
    jsocket

Misc
    export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/opt/HPCCSystems/lib;
